Masisa Weighs Colombia, Mexico Land Purchases, Mercurio Reports

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-03-09T12:41:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/masisa-weighs-colombia-mexico-land-purchases-mercurio-reports.html
  Masisa SA (MASISA) , the Santiago-based
forestry company, is considering buying land in  Colombia  and  Mexico , Chief Executive Officer Roberto Salas said in an
interview with  El Mercurio .  The company may acquire forested land in Colombia on its
own while in Mexico it may do so with a local partner, the
Santiago-based newspaper reported. Masisa owns land in  Brazil ,  Chile ,  Venezuela  and  Argentina , El Mercurio reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
